okes&#8230; A LOT!\nIt&#8217;s sticky, you just feel dirty touching it and when the fans start blowing&#8230; The [...]\";s:12:\"atom_content\";s:681:\"<p>Guess what this is:</p>\n<p><a href=\"http://meandmymac.net/wp-content/uploads/worldsdirtiestimac.jpg\"><img src=\"http://meandmymac.net/wp-content/uploads/worldsdirtiestimac-337x450.jpg\" alt=\"worldsdirtiestimac\" title=\"worldsdirtiestimac\" width=\"337\" height=\"450\" class=\"alignnone size-medium wp-image-757\" /></a></p>\n<p>Yup! That&#8217;s right, the backside of an 20&#8243; iMac LCD monitor. Except that it should be shiny, silvery and glimmery! This one looks as if it&#8217;s been on fire&#8230; Was it? No! The owner just smokes&#8230; A LOT!</p>\n<p>It&#8217;s sticky, you just feel dirty touching it and when the fans start blowing&#8230; The smell&#8230; Ew!</p>\n<p>Yuk!</p>\n\";}}s:7:\"channel\";a:8:{s:5:\"title\";s:13:\"Me and my Mac\";s:4:\"link\";s:21:\"http://meandmymac.net\";s:11:\"description\";s:33:\"Not just another WordPress weblog\";s:13:\"lastbuilddate\";s:31:\"Wed, 15 Jul 2009 20:21:50 +0000\";s:9:\"generator\";s:29:\"http://wordpress.org/?v=2.8.1\";s:8:\"language\";s:2:\"en\";s:2:\"sy\";a:2:{s:12:\"updateperiod\";s:6:\"hourly\";s:15:\"updatefrequency\";s:1:\"1\";}s:7:\"tagline\";s:33:\"Not just another WordPress weblog\";}s:9:\"textinput\";a:0:{}s:5:\"image\";a:0:{}s:9:\"feed_type\";s:3:\"RSS\";s:12:\"feed_version\";s:3:\"2.0\";s:5:\"stack\";a:0:{}s:9:\"inchannel\";b:0;s:6:\"initem\";b:0;s:9:\"incontent\";b:0;s:11:\"intextinput\";b:0;s:7:\"inimage\";b:0;s:13:\"current_field\";s:0:\"\";s:17:\"current_namespace\";b:0;s:19:\"_CONTENT_CONSTRUCTS\";a:6:{i:0;s:7:\"content\";i:1;s:7:\"summary\";i:2;s:4:\"info\";i:3;s:5:\"title\";i:4;s:7:\"tagline\";i:5;s:9:\"copyright\";}}','no'),(217,0,'tdomf_version_current','51','yes'),(218,0,'tdomf_enable_moderation','1','yes'),(219,0,'tdomf_preview','1','yes'),(220,0,'tdomf_trust_count','-1','yes'),(221,0,'tdomf_your_submissions','1','yes'),(222,0,'tdomf_fo